Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:12.52,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.32,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:26.66,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}傷を負った　世界を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:31.67,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}強く儚い果実
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:38.59,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}つきまとう　責任の重たさで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:43.10,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}熟れ落ちて　土へと還る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:46.02,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.77,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:52.98,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}この血の滾りを解放してけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:53.98,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そこにいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:58.90,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}衝突に戦々恐々　降り立つ堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:04.16,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}早々に早熟な実も　食らい尽くすの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:09.87,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}もがく度に　蒼穹に聴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:13.08,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}君を確かめた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:13.91,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あっけない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:17.71,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}無い無い　馴れ合い　有り余った慟哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:23.05,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}葛藤に混乱していく　今を生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:29.93,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,3)}それでもまだ　僕らは目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.48,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fs45\pos(960,54)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:34.11,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:36.82,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　何処まででも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.28,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}Follow me Follow you
